{"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"notebook":"AWS","section":"Gaming on AWS","page":{"id":"0-29f7b3576bc4d34ca35534041d04449f!1-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2130","self":"https://www.onenote.com/api/v1.0/me/notes/pages/0-29f7b3576bc4d34ca35534041d04449f!1-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2130","createdTime":"2017-10-24T01:58:26.364Z","title":"Gaming on AWS : 일본게임","createdByAppId":"","links":{"oneNoteEmbedUrl":{"href":"https://onedrive.live.com/redir.aspx?cid=bc575ab8e2ab9833&page=edit&resid=BC575AB8E2AB9833!2000&parId=BC575AB8E2AB9833!109&wd=target%28Gaming%20on%20AWS.one%7C51e5eaa8-700a-1840-b862-64d1d35ce5b9%2FGaming%20on%20AWS%20%20%EC%9D%BC%EB%B3%B8%EA%B2%8C%EC%9E%84%7C83e46495-5a43-3149-9351-d9debd747ce9%2F%29"},"oneNoteClientUrl":{"href":"onenote:https://d.docs.live.net/bc575ab8e2ab9833/Documents/AWS/Gaming%20on%20AWS.one#Gaming%20on%20AWS%20%20%EC%9D%BC%EB%B3%B8%EA%B2%8C%EC%9E%84&section-id=51e5eaa8-700a-1840-b862-64d1d35ce5b9&page-id=83e46495-5a43-3149-9351-d9debd747ce9&end"},"oneNoteWebUrl":{"href":"https://onedrive.live.com/redir.aspx?cid=bc575ab8e2ab9833&page=edit&resid=BC575AB8E2AB9833!2000&parId=BC575AB8E2AB9833!109&wd=target%28Gaming%20on%20AWS.one%7C51e5eaa8-700a-1840-b862-64d1d35ce5b9%2FGaming%20on%20AWS%20%20%EC%9D%BC%EB%B3%B8%EA%B2%8C%EC%9E%84%7C83e46495-5a43-3149-9351-d9debd747ce9%2F%29"}},"contentUrl":"https://www.onenote.com/api/v1.0/me/notes/pages/0-29f7b3576bc4d34ca35534041d04449f!1-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2130/content","lastModifiedTime":"2018-07-09T06:12:19Z","parentSection@odata.context":"https://www.onenote.com/api/v1.0/$metadata#me/notes/sections('0-BC575AB8E2AB9833%212130')/pages('0-29f7b3576bc4d34ca35534041d04449f%211-BC575AB8E2AB9833%212130')/parentSection(id,name,self)/$entity","parentSection":{"id":"0-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2130","name":"Gaming on AWS","self":"https://www.onenote.com/api/v1.0/me/notes/sections/0-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2130"},"content":"       다양한 유즈케이스들에 s3사용    Aurora : 게임 백엔드를 위한 기본컴포넌트로 인식        # 일본 게임사용사례    Large-scale Integration    DynamoDB를 활용해서 유지보수 비용 최소화    Ec2와 dynamodb의 오토스케일링기능을 활용함으로써 단한번도 리소스 부족이 일어나지 않았었다        # dynamoDB    상태를 저장해서 지속적으로 동기화하는 데에 썼다. -> 렉 없이 순조롭게 게임을 할 수 있다.    집계 분석이는 어울리지않는 데이터베이스이다. 로그적재에 사용하고 s3에 집어넣었다.        # 로그 적재방법 case    로그데이터 하루에 14TB 가 쌓임    AWS S3, SQS을 처음에 구현함    이후에는 Lambda 와 ECS, 오토스케일링으로 비용을 1/20 줄임        S3 트리거로 람다호출 -> 람다가 SQS로 저장    정기적으로 람다를 구동해서 필요한만큼의 ECS컨테이너를 구동하여 데이터 처리중.        # Aurora의 표준화    일본에서 많이 사용하는 MySQL과 100프로 호환됨             Grani        1명의 엔지니어가 초당 5000개의 리퀘스트를 처리하는 소셜게임시스템을 구축    140개의 EC2 , 6개의 RDS 사용        RDS on MySQL 응답시간 : 15~22ms    마이그레이션 이후    RDS on Aurora 응답시간 : 5.5ms    => MySQL보다 3배 빠른 성능             MYNET        4-pair MySQL shard with Fusion IO    Aurora 마이그레이션 후 82% 비용절감        # Lambda         Dragon quest X        썸네일 표시하는 기능에 대해..    10초 내에 18000개의 이미지처리제공    1/20 비용절감             Monster hunter explore        초기비용의 90%감소,     리드타임 수개월에서 수 분으로 감소        람다에서 Amazon Gamelift SDK를 호출해서 사용.       ","html":"\n\t\t<div style=\"position:absolute;left:12px;top:146px;width:624px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xB2E4;&#xC591;&#xD55C;</span><span lang=\"en-US\"> </span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC720;&#xC988;&#xCF00;&#xC774;&#xC2A4;&#xB4E4;&#xC5D0;</span><span lang=\"en-US\"> s3</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC0AC;&#xC6A9;</span></p>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">Aurora : &#xAC8C;&#xC784; &#xBC31;&#xC5D4;&#xB4DC;&#xB97C; &#xC704;&#xD55C; &#xAE30;&#xBCF8;&#xCEF4;&#xD3EC;&#xB10C;&#xD2B8;&#xB85C; &#xC778;&#xC2DD;</span></p>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"># &#xC77C;&#xBCF8; &#xAC8C;&#xC784;&#xC0AC;&#xC6A9;&#xC0AC;&#xB840;</span></p>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">Large-scale Integration</span></p>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">DynamoDB&#xB97C; &#xD65C;&#xC6A9;&#xD574;&#xC11C; &#xC720;&#xC9C0;&#xBCF4;&#xC218; &#xBE44;&#xC6A9; &#xCD5C;&#xC18C;&#xD654;</span></p>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">Ec2&#xC640; dynamodb&#xC758; &#xC624;&#xD1A0;&#xC2A4;&#xCF00;&#xC77C;&#xB9C1;&#xAE30;&#xB2A5;&#xC744; &#xD65C;&#xC6A9;&#xD568;&#xC73C;&#xB85C;&#xC368; &#xB2E8;&#xD55C;&#xBC88;&#xB3C4; &#xB9AC;&#xC18C;&#xC2A4; &#xBD80;&#xC871;&#xC774; &#xC77C;&#xC5B4;&#xB098;&#xC9C0; &#xC54A;&#xC558;&#xC5C8;&#xB2E4;</span></p>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"># dynamoDB</span></p>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC0C1;&#xD0DC;&#xB97C; &#xC800;&#xC7A5;&#xD574;&#xC11C; &#xC9C0;&#xC18D;&#xC801;&#xC73C;&#xB85C; &#xB3D9;&#xAE30;&#xD654;&#xD558;&#xB294; &#xB370;&#xC5D0; &#xC37C;&#xB2E4;. -&gt; &#xB809; &#xC5C6;&#xC774; &#xC21C;&#xC870;&#xB86D;&#xAC8C; &#xAC8C;&#xC784;&#xC744; &#xD560; &#xC218; &#xC788;&#xB2E4;.</span></p>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC9D1;&#xACC4; &#xBD84;&#xC11D;&#xC774;&#xB294; &#xC5B4;&#xC6B8;&#xB9AC;&#xC9C0;&#xC54A;&#xB294; &#xB370;&#xC774;&#xD130;&#xBCA0;&#xC774;&#xC2A4;&#xC774;&#xB2E4;. &#xB85C;&#xADF8;&#xC801;&#xC7AC;&#xC5D0; &#xC0AC;&#xC6A9;&#xD558;&#xACE0; s3&#xC5D0; &#xC9D1;&#xC5B4;&#xB123;&#xC5C8;&#xB2E4;.</span></p>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"># &#xB85C;&#xADF8; &#xC801;&#xC7AC;&#xBC29;&#xBC95; case</span></p>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xB85C;&#xADF8;&#xB370;&#xC774;&#xD130; &#xD558;&#xB8E8;&#xC5D0; 14TB &#xAC00; &#xC313;&#xC784;</span></p>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">AWS S3, SQS&#xC744; &#xCC98;&#xC74C;&#xC5D0; &#xAD6C;&#xD604;&#xD568;</span></p>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC774;&#xD6C4;&#xC5D0;&#xB294; Lambda &#xC640; ECS, &#xC624;&#xD1A0;&#xC2A4;&#xCF00;&#xC77C;&#xB9C1;&#xC73C;&#xB85C; &#xBE44;&#xC6A9;&#xC744; 1/20 &#xC904;&#xC784;</span></p>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">S3 &#xD2B8;&#xB9AC;&#xAC70;&#xB85C; &#xB78C;&#xB2E4;&#xD638;&#xCD9C; -&gt; &#xB78C;&#xB2E4;&#xAC00; SQS&#xB85C; &#xC800;&#xC7A5;</span></p>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC815;&#xAE30;&#xC801;&#xC73C;&#xB85C; &#xB78C;&#xB2E4;&#xB97C; &#xAD6C;&#xB3D9;&#xD574;&#xC11C; &#xD544;&#xC694;&#xD55C;&#xB9CC;&#xD07C;&#xC758; ECS&#xCEE8;&#xD14C;&#xC774;&#xB108;&#xB97C; &#xAD6C;&#xB3D9;&#xD558;&#xC5EC; &#xB370;&#xC774;&#xD130; &#xCC98;&#xB9AC;&#xC911;.</span></p>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"># Aurora<span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC758;</span> <span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xD45C;&#xC900;&#xD654;</span></p>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC77C;&#xBCF8;&#xC5D0;&#xC11C; &#xB9CE;&#xC774; &#xC0AC;&#xC6A9;&#xD558;&#xB294; MySQL&#xACFC; 100&#xD504;&#xB85C; &#xD638;&#xD658;&#xB428;</span></p>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span lang=\"en-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">Grani</span></span></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">1&#xBA85;&#xC758; &#xC5D4;&#xC9C0;&#xB2C8;&#xC5B4;&#xAC00; &#xCD08;&#xB2F9; 5000&#xAC1C;&#xC758; &#xB9AC;&#xD018;&#xC2A4;&#xD2B8;&#xB97C; &#xCC98;&#xB9AC;&#xD558;&#xB294; &#xC18C;&#xC15C;&#xAC8C;&#xC784;&#xC2DC;&#xC2A4;&#xD15C;&#xC744; &#xAD6C;&#xCD95;</span></p>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">140&#xAC1C;&#xC758; EC2 , 6&#xAC1C;&#xC758; RDS &#xC0AC;&#xC6A9;</span></p>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">RDS on MySQL <span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC751;&#xB2F5;&#xC2DC;&#xAC04;</span> : 15~22ms</p>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xB9C8;&#xC774;&#xADF8;&#xB808;&#xC774;&#xC158;</span> <span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC774;&#xD6C4;</span></p>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">RDS on Aurora <span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC751;&#xB2F5;&#xC2DC;&#xAC04;</span> : 5.5ms</p>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">=&gt; MySQL<span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xBCF4;&#xB2E4;</span> 3<span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xBC30;</span> <span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xBE60;&#xB978;</span> <span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC131;&#xB2A5;</span></p>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span lang=\"en-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">MYNET</span></span></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">4-pair MySQL shard with Fusion IO</span></p>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">Aurora &#xB9C8;&#xC774;&#xADF8;&#xB808;&#xC774;&#xC158; &#xD6C4; 82% &#xBE44;&#xC6A9;&#xC808;&#xAC10;</span></p>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"># Lambda</span></p>\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span lang=\"en-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">Dragon quest X</span></span></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC378;&#xB124;&#xC77C; &#xD45C;&#xC2DC;&#xD558;&#xB294; &#xAE30;&#xB2A5;&#xC5D0; &#xB300;&#xD574;..</span></p>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">10&#xCD08; &#xB0B4;&#xC5D0; 18000&#xAC1C;&#xC758; &#xC774;&#xBBF8;&#xC9C0;&#xCC98;&#xB9AC;&#xC81C;&#xACF5;</span></p>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">1/20 &#xBE44;&#xC6A9;&#xC808;&#xAC10;</span></p>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span lang=\"en-US\">Monster hunter explore</span></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xCD08;&#xAE30;&#xBE44;&#xC6A9;&#xC758;</span> 90%<span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xAC10;&#xC18C;</span>, </p>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xB9AC;&#xB4DC;&#xD0C0;&#xC784;</span> <span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC218;&#xAC1C;&#xC6D4;&#xC5D0;&#xC11C;</span> <span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC218;</span> <span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xBD84;&#xC73C;&#xB85C;</span> <span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xAC10;&#xC18C;</span></p>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<p style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xB78C;&#xB2E4;&#xC5D0;&#xC11C;</span><span lang=\"en-US\"> Amazon Gamelift SDK</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xB97C;</span><span lang=\"en-US\"> </span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xD638;&#xCD9C;&#xD574;&#xC11C;</span><span lang=\"en-US\"> </span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC0AC;&#xC6A9;</span><span lang=\"en-US\">.</span></p>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\n\n"}}}